OL,5, The current BBC licence fee of #159    
OL,6, will increase by #10.50 - a rise of    
OL,7, 6.6% - the government has announced.   
OL,9,FThe figure has been determined using   
OL,10,FSeptember's rate of inflation, rather  
OL,11,Fthan an average across the last year.  
OL,13,FDue to the recent fall in inflation,   
OL,14,Fthat means the #169.50 figure is less  
OL,15,Fthan the BBC and Office for Budget     
OL,16,FResponsibility (OBR) had anticipated.  
OL,18,FThe decision to raise it by a smaller  
OL,19,Fpercentage will leave a expected       
OL,20,Ffunding gap of around #90m.            
